# Naryn, Khorinsky District, Republic of Buryatia

}}
Naryn (; , Narin) is a rural locality (a settlement) in Khorinsky District, Republic of Buryatia, Russia. The population was 171 as of 2010. There are two streets.
Geography
Naryn is located 44&nbsp;km west of Khorinsk (the district's administrative centre) by road. Tarbagatay is the nearest rural locality.
